                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i5.12">
                    <locus from="74r"/>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">ከመዝ፡ ጥንተ፡ ሕንጸቱ፡ ለቤተ፡ ክርስቲያኑ፡ ለጊዮርጊስ፡ በልዳ፡ ወታአምር፡ ዘአርአየ፡ በእንተ፡ ዐምደ፡ መበለት፡ ባርክ፡ እግዚኦ፡ አሜን።</hi></incipit>
                        
                        <title type="complete" xml:lang="en" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6220MGPillar">Eleventh miracle</title>
